Pwani Oil Group has launched a new cooking oil product &mdash; Salit &mdash; with non-drip spout that will save oil usually lost when it drips.Commercial director Raju Malde said the product will serve the changing consumer needs.The company said it spent Sh15 million in the last one year and four months to invent and innovate the product that is second to Fresh Fry, its other product.Salit is packaged in various sizes from 500ml bottles up to 20-litre jerricans.